Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pakkun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop all of the sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting farther away at a rapid rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent of Sasuke and two others, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.66,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like Sasuke is going after those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The others show no signs of moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't waste time here! Let's go after Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But what...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining guys are about to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We must take a longer route to avoid them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If we do that, it will take longer to catch up to Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what will happen in a combat area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that we will get dragged into a battle, even if we do not wish to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, our mission is to bring Sasuke back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to do that, we must avoid engagements as much as possible until we complete that mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.83,TLnote,,0,0,0,,(Kugutsu no Jutsu: Puppet Technique)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kugutsu no Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am from Konoha's Aburame clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if our enemy is a small bug, we will not underestimate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fight with everything we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down, Temari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you move again, Gaara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro should be delaying the Uchiha right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this chance to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry, or the plan will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Temari, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:40.39,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(465,226)}Astonishment! Gaara's true identity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Astonishment! Gaara's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The blade is poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Uchiha Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he get past Kankuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he came here too fast to have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Another pursuer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you Sand guys are planning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will determine what your true identity is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,going to awaken {\i1}it{\i0} right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding! I won't be able to control him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Gaara! Did you forget the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You are called Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You have goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You are similar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,By killing you, I can exist in this world as the one who erased your existence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be able to feel that I am alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your location is obvious with that intense bloodlust of yours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is your goal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you seek power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't concern you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get lost. You're interrupting my training.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You... have the same eyes as I have.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eyes that seek power and are filled with hate and bloodlust.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are similar to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't forget, you are my...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It has begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You made a clone with bugs and sneaked behind me... Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a puppeteer who favors medium to long range battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect that your weakness lies in close combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,since that Kugutsu no Jutsu of yours requires concentration to control the puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes the user vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a puppeteer's weak point well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I'll show you the true use of this Ninjutsu in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The true strength of the tactical puppet Karasu, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... a poison gas bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I inhaled a small amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So the user will now hide himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if an enemy ninja appears, do not panic. Hide yourselves in the secret room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jounin and Chuunin teachers will protect you with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Konohamaru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's working hard out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They can push the enemy back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a crack in one of the carved stones of Hokage-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.49,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Old geezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come this far... I've come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, do I not have enough strength left to pull this guy's soul out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that sacrificing my life is not enough with this old body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have killed me if you were ten years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarutobi, if you don't defeat this man now, the village will perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You... half-dead corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... let me feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That eye I saw before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like it won't end by the time you come here to back me up, Shino.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the poison is spreading now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bugs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But in his state, he shouldn't be able to move around a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll free you from your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I slipped bugs into all of his joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He stuffed bugs into the joints to make it immovable?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he plan to do that from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The bugs are moving along the chakra strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They feed on chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He will find my location at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He cut his chakra strings off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting chakra strings that have been detached back to normal in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is an easy task for a first-rate puppeteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And in each individual part of Karasu's body there are weapons installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an armed puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think that you've won by just stopping his movement you've made a big mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a lot of poison on that needle tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When did the bugs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.77,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My chakra strings have been eaten off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did these bugs come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You let your guard down after getting rid of the decoy bugs that moved along the chakra strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you failed to notice the bugs who were swarming behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:19:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The bugs were moving the entire time, heading for your forehead protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That last attack, I pretended to fail to hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I attached a bug to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you find out my location from just this single bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like to explain the same thing twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shino.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before you left the stadium, I put a female bug on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The female is almost odorless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only things that can smell that faint female scent are the males of the same species.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the bug on my forehead is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison has spread throughout my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.30,0:20:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that I cannot be your reinforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, Uchiha Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchiha Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of my existence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchiha Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Prey!
